data.description:
This home boasts  touches at every turn, including elegant arched doorways, soaring vaulted ceilings, and cozy fireplaces in both the living room and master bedroom. The kitchen, entryway, and laundry room are adorned with beautiful 18' tile. Plus, you'll find ceiling fans throughout for added comfort. Step into the backyard and discover a sparkling play pool and two inviting covered patios, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Inside, a vast loft or game room offers endless possibilities. The large master suite features his and hers closets and a relaxing jetted tub for ultimate luxury. With two efficient A/C units, (one new) energy efficiency is a priority in this remarkable home. 
Newer roof 2021 .
